title: USGS NED Original Product Resolution (OPR) Downloadable Data Collection
name: usgs-ned-original-product-resolution-opr-downloadable-data-collection
notes: This data collection is the Original Product Resolution (OPR) Digital Elevation Model (DEM) as provided to the USGS. This DEM is delivered in the original resolution, with the original spatial reference. All elevation units have been converted to meters. These data may be used as the source of updates to the National Elevation Dataset (NED), which serves as the elevation layer of the National Map.
